These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, june, march
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, prince, chaman, cain
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, amaryllis, lily
 1. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
 2. the person who growsmarigold is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
 3. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the bolivar-smoker is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8
 5. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the person who growsmarigold##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who growstulip and the prince-smoker##2
 9. the person who growslily is the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who growsamaryllis##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the prince-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Birthday   | february | march   | may   | june  |
| Cigar         | prince  | chaman  | cain  | bolivar |
| Flower     | marigold    | amaryllis | tulip     | lily    |

