 5. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the tower house##8
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
11. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the tower house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
17. the craftsman house is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
19. the tower house is on the right of the person who growslily##1

