There are 4 different nationalities: polish, brazilian, american, mexican
 1. the polish is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 4. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 5. the american is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 6. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
 7. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the brazilian is on the far right##1
11. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
12. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
