City: paris, nizza, san-francisco, new-york
 1. the colonial house is not the fan of indie##6
 2. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 3. the person eating plum is the fan of classical##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the fan of indie and the fan of disco##2
 5. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 6. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
 8. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
 9. the victorian house is on the right of the fan of pop##1
10. the fan of disco is the person traveling to paris##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
13. the colonial house is on the right of the wooden house##1
14. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
15. the wooden house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
