4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, mouse, dog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
 2. the owner of the dog is the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who growsazalea##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 5. the person who likes orange is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who likes orange##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
 8. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
10. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the person who likes orange##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who growsaconite and the person who likes grey##2
12. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
