.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Transport           | quad-bike | ship       | subway      | airplane  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
| Hobby   | woodworking   | drawing          | traveling      | photography  |
| Sport   | climbing   | sailing      | cricket | cycling |

